Titolo: Koumajou Densetsu: Scarlet Symphony

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Koumajou Densetsu: Scarlet Symphony (紅魔城伝説 緋色の交響曲) is a Metroidvania Touhou Project fangame developed in 2009 for Microsoft Windows. The game has also been referred to as 'Touhouvania'.A remaster, titled Koumajou Remilia: Scarlet Symphony (紅魔城レミリア 緋色の交響曲), was announced in 2021, which is planned to release the same year on Steam and Nintendo Switch.